<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Convert2PDF</title>

    <!-- Fontes -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    
    <!-- Style.css externo -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
    <!-- Header com Navbar-->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-sm">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light container">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Convert2PDF</a>
                <!-- Quando a largura da tela diminuir até certo ponto, as opções da navbar vai ser substituídas por um botão colapsável que exibe os atalhos ao clicar -->
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                    <!-- Define os atalhos da navbar -->
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Início</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/image-to-pdf">Imagem para PDF</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/combinar-pdf">Combinar PDF</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/faq">FAQ</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                        <% if (user) { %>
                            <a href="/painel" class="btn btn-primary">Painel</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Entrar</a>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <!-- Seção Hero -->
        <section class="pt-5 text-center container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="fw-bold">Suas ferramentas de PDF Simples e Rápidas</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-muted">Converta imagens ou combine múltiplos PDFs em um único arquivo com apenas alguns cliques.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Seção de cards das Ferramentas -->
        <section class="py-5 bg-light">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">

                    <!-- Card 1: Imagem para PDF -->
                    <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8">
                        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0 text-center tool-card">
                            <div class="card-body p-5">
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <img src="images/images-icon.svg"
                                    width="64" height="64" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-image-fill text-primary" viewBox="0 0 16 16" alt="Icon of a collection of images">
                                </div>
                                <h3 class="card-title fw-bold mb-3">Imagem para PDF</h3>
                                <p class="card-text text-muted mb-4">Converta arquivos JPG, PNG e TIFF em um documento PDF.</p>
                                <a href="/image-to-pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Acessar Ferramenta</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Card 2: Combinar PDF -->
                    <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8">
                        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0 text-center tool-card">
                            <div class="card-body p-5">
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-files text-primary" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M13 0H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h7a2 2 0 0 0 2-2 2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 13V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h7a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v10a1 1 0 0 1-1 1M3 4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h7a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v10a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1z"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <h3 class="card-title fw-bold">Combinar PDFs</h3>
                                <p class="card-text text-muted mb-4">Junte e organize vários arquivos PDF em um único documento.</p>
                                <a href="/image-to-pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Acessar Ferramenta</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Seção de descrição breve -->
        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row text-center g-4">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill text-primary mb-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 0c-.69 0-1.843.265-2.928.56-1.11.3-2.229.655-2.887.87a1.54 1.54 0 0 0-1.044 1.262c-.596 4.477.787 7.795 2.465 9.99a11.8 11.8 0 0 0 2.517 2.453c.386.273.744.482 1.048.625.28.132.581.24.829.24s.548-.108.829-.24a7 7 0 0 0 1.048-.625 11.8 11.8 0 0 0 2.517-2.453c1.678-2.195 3.061-5.513 2.465-9.99a1.54 1.54 0 0 0-1.044-1.263 63 63 0 0 0-2.887-.87C9.843.266 8.69 0 8 0m0 5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 .5 2.915l.385 1.99a.5.5 0 0 1-.491.595h-.788a.5.5 0 0 1-.49-.595l.384-1.99A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 8 5"/></svg>
                        <h3 class="h4">Seguro e Privado</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Seus arquivos são processados com segurança e deletados de nossos servidores permanentemente após uma hora.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-speedometer2 text-primary mb-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V6a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0V4.5A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4zM3.732 5.732a.5.5 0 0 1 .707 0l.915.914a.5.5 0 1 1-.708.708l-.914-.915a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.707zM2 10a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1.586a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H2.5A.5.5 0 0 1 2 10zm9.5 0a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1.5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H12a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5zm.754-4.246a.389.389 0 0 0-.527-.02L7.547 9.31a.91.91 0 1 0 1.302 1.258l3.434-4.297a.389.389 0 0 0-.029-.518z"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M0 10a8 8 0 1 1 15.547 2.661c-.442 1.253-1.845 1.602-2.932 1.25C11.309 13.488 9.475 13 8 13c-1.474 0-3.31.488-4.615.911-1.087.352-2.49.003-2.932-1.25A7.988 7.988 0 0 1 0 10zm8-7a7 7 0 0 0-6.603 9.329c.203.575.923.876 1.68.63C4.397 12.533 6.358 12 8 12s3.604.532 4.923.86c.757.245 1.477-.056 1.68-.631A7 7 0 0 0 8 3z"/></svg>
                        <h3 class="h4">Conversão Rápida</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Nossos servidores poderosos convertem seus arquivos em segundos, sem comprometer a qualidade.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-box2-heart-fill text-primary mb-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3.75 0a1 1 0 0 0-.8.4L.1 4.2a.5.5 0 0 0-.1.3V15a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h14a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V4.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.1-.3L13.05.4a1 1 0 0 0-.8-.4zM8.5 4h6l.5.667V5H1v-.333L1.5 4h6V1h1zM8 7.993c1.664-1.711 5.825 1.283 0 5.132-5.825-3.85-1.664-6.843 0-5.132"/></svg>
                        <h3 class="h4">Totalmente Gratuito</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Converta quantos arquivos quiser. Nosso serviço é gratuito e não requer cadastro ou instalação.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>